title: Annual Progress Report of the Detroit River International Wildlife Refuge and the International Wildlife Refuge Alliance 2007 Calendar Year
name: annual-progress-report-of-the-detroit-river-international-wildlife-refuge-and-the-internat-2c7cb
notes: This annual narrative report for Detroit River International Wildlife Refuge summarizes Refuge activities during the 2007 calendar year. The report begins with a letter from Congressman John Dingell. Followed by an introduction to the Refuge and a summary of habitat conservation efforts.  Information about research and monitoring including biological surveys for Grassy Island . Community engagement efforts are discussed along with capacity building efforts. Lastly, upcoming activities and investments are summarized.
